To generate one or more texts about the Greek exhibits, where exhibit names range from exhibit1 to exhibit50
If you generate multiple exhibits in one call, you will get comparisons and proper referring expressions.

cd data
./reload-domain-xml mpiro-methodius-config.xml
./run-methodius-xml -c mpiro-methodius-config.xml [exhibit1] [numfacts1] [exhibit2] [numfacts2] ...